  "text": "In this section the model used to calculate the trajectories of central plasma sheet Algorithm 1 Global constants and variables used by other algorithms, and names of parameters passed to functions and procedures given in other algorithms. (CPS) particles in the inner magnetosphere under conditions of steady convection is described. The model follows the same method and assumptions used by [CITATION_1] . It assumes a dipole geomagnetic field aligned with the Earth's spin axis and having equipotential field lines. The co-rotation electric field potential is then taken as",
